Text: RE Your sons first gamei would probably be in the restroom at halftime a little longer than usual if yall know what i mean Original Message From Newman Michael mailto Sent Tuesday November AM To Joey Sciortino Subject RE Your sons first game IS THAT A BEER IN FRONT OF THE KID BEAUTIFUL Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday November AM To Newman Michael Subject Re Your sons first game I didnt know Cleveland can get that quality of fans The kid loves it Go Browns JPM
